      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Discussion: Informal settlements — slums — often have many positive qualities, including existing neighborhood relationships, cultural creativity, resource efficiency, and remarkable levels of innovation and resourcefulness. But they often also lack mobility and access, good utility service, sanitation, security, and other essential conditions necessary for quality of life.",
      "id": "13221378657823"
